.TH LSSA 1 "December 2024" "LSSA 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lssa \- Live Source Sync Assistant
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lssa
[\fIDIRECTORY\fR]
.br
.B lssa stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
LSSA is an intelligent backup system that monitors file changes in real-time
and integrates with git to manage backups automatically.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B [DIRECTORY]
Watch specified directory (default: current directory)
.TP
.B stats
Display file activity heatmap
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Start monitoring:
.B lssa
.TP
View activity heatmap:
.B lssa stats
.SH AUTHOR
LSSA Development Team
